{% doc %}
  About page body content for Moon Style Apparel (rendered by msa-static-page).
{% enddoc %}

<div class="section msa-about" style="--section-pt: 20px; --section-pb: 60px;">
  <div class="fluid_container">
    <div class="msa-about__hero">
      <div class="msa-about__hero-content">
        <p class="msa-about__eyebrow">Est. 2012 — UK based</p>
        <h2 class="msa-about__heading">About Moon Style Apparel</h2>
        <div class="msa-about__text rte">
          <p>Established in 2012, Moon Style Apparel is a UK-based online fashion retailer dedicated to delivering stylish, comfortable, and high-quality clothing for everyday living. We believe fashion should be accessible, responsibly made, and designed to inspire confidence in every customer.</p>
          <p>From wardrobe essentials to seasonal favourites, our collections combine timeless style with modern trends, offering versatile pieces for every occasion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__hero-media">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Clothing rails inside a modern apparel store"
          loading="lazy"
          width="960"
          height="640"
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__split msa-about__split--reverse">
      <div class="msa-about__split-media">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558769132-cb1aea458c5e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Fashion designer working with fabric swatches"
          loading="lazy"
          width="720"
          height="540"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__split-content">
        <h3 class="msa-about__title">Our story</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__text rte">
          <p>Moon Style Apparel was founded with a simple vision: to create clothing that looks great, feels comfortable, and offers exceptional value without compromising on quality or responsibility.</p>
          <p>Over the years, we have built long-term relationships with trusted manufacturing partners and suppliers, allowing us to maintain consistent quality while continually expanding our collections to meet the evolving needs of our customers.</p>
          <p>Whether you're shopping for everyday basics, statement pieces, or seasonal essentials, our goal is to provide clothing you'll enjoy wearing for years to come.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__block msa-about__block--wide">
      <h3 class="msa-about__title msa-about__title--center">Designed with quality in mind</h3>
      <div class="msa-about__text msa-about__text--center rte">
        <p>Every garment is carefully selected and produced with attention to detail, comfort, and durability. Our collections include:</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="msa-about__chips list-unstyled">
        <li class="msa-about__chip">T-Shirts &amp; Graphic Tees</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Camis &amp; Tank Tops</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Hoodies &amp; Sweatshirts</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Button Front Shirts</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Polos</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Sweaters &amp; Cardigans</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Jeans</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Trousers</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Shorts</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Jackets &amp; Coats</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Sweatpants</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">Seasonal Collections</li>
        <li class="msa-about__chip">New Arrivals</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="msa-about__note">We continuously update our range to bring fresh styles while maintaining the quality our customers expect.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__split">
      <div class="msa-about__split-media">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591195853828-11db59a44f6b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Spools of thread at a garment manufacturing facility"
          loading="lazy"
          width="720"
          height="540"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__split-content">
        <h3 class="msa-about__title">Our manufacturing</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__text rte">
          <p>Quality begins long before a product reaches our customers. Our garments are produced through our experienced manufacturing partner, <strong>Moon Style Textile</strong>, where skilled teams combine modern production techniques with strict quality control standards.</p>
          <p>With years of expertise in garment manufacturing, we oversee every stage of production to ensure consistency, craftsmanship, and reliability. By working closely with our manufacturing operations, we maintain greater control over product quality, ethical production, and customer satisfaction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__block msa-about__block--wide msa-about__cards-heading">
      <h3 class="msa-about__title msa-about__title--center">Sustainability</h3>
      <div class="msa-about__text msa-about__text--center rte">
        <p>We understand that the future of fashion depends on making responsible choices. Sustainability is an ongoing journey, and we continue to improve our practices across every part of our business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__cards grid grid-cols gap" style="--col-desktop: 4; --col-tablet: 2; --col-number: 1;">
      <div class="msa-about__card">
        <h3 class="msa-about__card-title">Organic cotton</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__card-text rte">
          <p>Where possible, we incorporate organic cotton into our collections. Organic cotton is grown using farming practices that reduce the use of synthetic chemicals while supporting healthier ecosystems and producing naturally soft, comfortable fabrics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__card">
        <h3 class="msa-about__card-title">Recycled polyester</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__card-text rte">
          <p>We increasingly use recycled polyester to help reduce waste and conserve valuable natural resources. Giving existing materials a second life contributes to a more sustainable fashion industry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__card">
        <h3 class="msa-about__card-title">Responsible sourcing</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__card-text rte">
          <p>We work with suppliers and manufacturing partners who share our commitment to ethical business practices, quality workmanship, safe working conditions, and responsible production standards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__card">
        <h3 class="msa-about__card-title">Less waste</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__card-text rte">
          <p>We continually review our production and packaging processes to reduce unnecessary waste — from improving operational efficiency to using more sustainable materials where possible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__split msa-about__split--reverse">
      <div class="msa-about__split-media">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737711867-e3b97375f902?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Team members working together around a table"
          loading="lazy"
          width="720"
          height="540"
        >
      </div>
      <div class="msa-about__split-content">
        <h3 class="msa-about__title">Ethics</h3>
        <div class="msa-about__text rte">
          <p>Respect, fairness, and integrity guide every decision we make.</p>
          <p>We support ethical manufacturing practices and believe everyone involved in creating our products deserves safe working conditions, fair treatment, and respect. We are committed to building long-term relationships with partners who share these values.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__highlight">
      <p class="msa-about__eyebrow msa-about__eyebrow--light">Our commitment</p>
      <h3 class="msa-about__highlight-title">Charitable partner — SAVE DC</h3>
      <div class="msa-about__highlight-text rte">
        <p>At Moon Style Apparel, we believe businesses should create a positive impact beyond fashion. Supporting communities and investing in brighter futures is an important part of who we are.</p>
        <p>We are proud to support <strong>SAVE DC</strong>, an organisation dedicated to transforming lives through education. Their mission focuses on expanding educational opportunities, empowering individuals, and helping communities build a stronger future.</p>
        <p>By partnering with SAVE DC, we are honoured to contribute to initiatives that create meaningful and lasting change through the power of education.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__block msa-about__block--wide">
      <h3 class="msa-about__title msa-about__title--center">Why choose Moon Style Apparel?</h3>
      <ul class="msa-about__checklist list-unstyled">
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Established in 2012</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>UK-based online fashion retailer</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>High-quality garments at competitive prices</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Trusted manufacturing expertise</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>New collections added regularly</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Commitment to ethical and responsible sourcing</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Focus on sustainability and reducing waste</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Secure online shopping and reliable customer service</span></li>
        <li class="msa-about__check-item"><span class="msa-about__check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Proud supporter of educational and community initiatives</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="msa-about__closing">
      <h3 class="msa-about__title msa-about__title--center">Looking ahead</h3>
      <div class="msa-about__text msa-about__text--center rte">
        <p>As we continue to grow, our commitment remains the same: creating quality clothing, embracing responsible business practices, and providing an exceptional shopping experience for every customer.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Moon Style Apparel. We're proud to be part of your wardrobe and look forward to serving you for many years to come.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .msa-about {
    padding-top: var(--section-pt, 40px);
    padding-bottom: var(--section-pb, 60px);
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .msa-about__eyebrow {
    color: #e85d04;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .msa-about__eyebrow--light {
    color: #ffb98a;
  }

  .msa-about__heading {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a3a6b;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.12;
  }

  .msa-about__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a3a6b;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .msa-about__title--center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .msa-about__text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #333;
  }

  .msa-about__text--center {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .msa-about__text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  }

  .msa-about__block {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .msa-about__block--wide {
    max-width: 1080px;
  }

  .msa-about__hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(0, 0.95fr);
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    max-width: 1160px;
  }

  .msa-about__hero-media img,
  .msa-about__split-media img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .msa-about__hero-media {
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 0 #f2e8df;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .msa-about__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    max-width: 1160px;
  }

  .msa-about__split--reverse .msa-about__split-media {
    order: 2;
  }

  .msa-about__split--reverse .msa-about__split-content {
    order: 1;
  }

  .msa-about__split-media {
    align-self: stretch;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .msa-about__chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2.4rem 0 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .msa-about__chip {
    background: #f8f9fb;
    border: 1px solid #dfe5ee;
    color: #1a3a6b;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    padding: 1rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .msa-about__note {
    text-align: center;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin: 2.4rem auto 0;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .msa-about__cards-heading {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .msa-about__cards {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
  }

  .msa-about__card {
    background: #f8f9fb;
    border: 1px solid #e8ecf2;
    border-top: 3px solid #e85d04;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .msa-about__card-title {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a3a6b;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .msa-about__card-text {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #444;
  }

  .msa-about__highlight {
    background: #1a3a6b;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5.6rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    max-width: 1160px;
  }

  .msa-about__highlight-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .msa-about__highlight-text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #d9e2f2;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .msa-about__highlight-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  }

  .msa-about__highlight-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .msa-about__checklist {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.4rem 3rem;
    margin: 2.8rem auto 0;
    padding: 0;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .msa-about__check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #333;
  }

  .msa-about__check-icon {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    margin-top: 0.3em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #e85d04;
    position: relative;
  }

  .msa-about__check-icon::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 5px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 4px;
    height: 8px;
    border: solid #fff;
    border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .msa-about__closing {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf2;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .msa-about__hero,
    .msa-about__split {
      gap: 2.8rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .msa-about__hero,
    .msa-about__split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .msa-about__hero-media {
      order: -1;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .msa-about__split--reverse .msa-about__split-media,
    .msa-about__split-media {
      order: -1;
    }

    .msa-about__checklist {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .msa-about__block {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
